    <content>&lt;P&gt;I need some help resolving an issue with downloading the agent for SAP BTP. Any assistance would be greatly appreciated.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="EugeneGarcia_0-1740100756855.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/228368i174CE163FCE55427/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="EugeneGarcia_0-1740100756855.png" alt="EugeneGarcia_0-1740100756855.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="EugeneGarcia_1-1740100778654.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/228369iD1A3B8B059D57B4C/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="EugeneGarcia_1-1740100778654.png" alt="EugeneGarcia_1-1740100778654.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;We have renewed the Secret ID in RBSC and tried creating another user; however, the issue still persists.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Upon checking SAP Note &lt;A href="https://me.sap.com/notes/0003387166" target="_new" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;0003387166&lt;/A&gt;, point number 2 indicates that we do not have an assigned license for SBPA or IRPA. I am unsure how to obtain this license.&lt;/P&gt;</content>
